{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_016DgdYaFDdfTHWjVrKFga7E","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The ES pods' readiness probe also reads from the `elastic-password` secret! When I rotated the password in ES and then updated the secret, the existing pods didn't pick up the new password since the secret was already mounted. Wait, they do pick up the new password from the secret because I've already patched `elastic-password` to have the new value.\n\nActually wait - the pods were running before and using `ELASTIC_PASSWORD` from the secret `elastic-password`. The secret previously contained `elasticpass`. I changed the ES password to `elasticpass-elastic-password-next` and then updated the secret. But the ES pods pick up the new secret value...\nKubernetes automatically updates mounted secrets within a few seconds to minutes, so the ES pods should eventually get the new password. The issue is that right now they might still be using the old one while the update propagates, causing their readiness probes to fail since the password they're using no longer matches what's actually set in Elasticsearch. Let me trace through this more carefully: the pods have `ELASTIC_PASSWORD` from the secret, which was `elasticpass`, then I changed the ES password to `elasticpass-elastic-password-next` and updated the secret to match, but the environment variable...\n\nActually, environment variables from secrets don't update automatically in running pods—only volume mounts do, and even those have a delay. The ES pods are still reading `ELASTIC_PASSWORD` as an env var with the old value, so they're still trying to authenticate with `elasticpass` while ES now requires the new password, which is why the readiness probes are failing. This cascades: unhealthy ES pods mean no endpoints, so the auth-checker can't connect either. I need to restart the ES pods to pick up the new secret value, but I should do a rolling restart to avoid downtime.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1003,"cache_read_input_tokens":35453,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1003},"output_tokens":19,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"78a83d6a-22b1-438b-b4b0-709b5aa6c4a3","uuid":"8e123c9a-0d11-4673-bb98-674face011e0","request_id":"req_011Ccf18JTXfDPUYDZE5PekM"}
